title: 110: 2016 NFL Jenga Pieces
itunes:title: 110: 2016 NFL Jenga Pieces
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks debate what team is the greatest threat to the Patriots in the AFC East. The guys then go team by team and decide what player each franchise can’t afford to lose. DJ and Bucky then take you inside a scout’s job during preseason games
